# Pipeline: Historical Stick Figure Prompt Generation

Nghiên cứu và đề xuất quy trình tạo prompt cho kịch bản lịch sử dạng stick figure (OverSimplified).

---

## Flow hiện tại (có vấn đề)

```
SRT files → [Mode Verify] → [Visual Bible] → [Group by interval] → [AI: Generate prompt] → CSV
                                  ↑ 
                          Chỉ mô tả chung,
                          không chuẩn hoá nhân vật
```

**Vấn đề:** Visual Bible hiện tại mô tả nhân vật kiểu "Physical: age, build, face, hair..." — quá chi tiết cho style stick figure. Cần chuẩn hoá theo 4 thuộc tính.

---

## Flow đề xuất (6 bước)

```
                ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
                │                  INPUT: SRT files               │
                └───────────────────┬─────────────────────────────┘
                                    ▼
              ┌─ STEP 1: Mode Detection ──────────────────────────┐
              │  AI verify: Independent / Narrative               │
              └───────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                                  ▼
              ┌─ STEP 2: Character Bible ─────────────────────────┐
              │  AI phân tích toàn bộ SRT                         │
              │  → Liệt kê nhân vật + 4 thuộc tính visual        │
              │  → Phân loại: Protagonist / Named / Archetype     │
              │  → Liệt kê locations + props theo chapter         │
              │  Output: character_bible.txt                      │
              └───────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                                  ▼
              ┌─ STEP 3: Character Sheet Prompts (optional) ──────┐
              │  Với mỗi Protagonist + Named character:           │
              │  → Tạo prompt cho character reference sheet        │
              │  Output: character_sheets.txt                     │
              │  (User dùng prompts này gen ảnh reference riêng)  │
              └───────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                                  ▼
              ┌─ STEP 4: Group SRT by interval ───────────────────┐
              │  SRT → Groups (6s, 8s, 10s...)                    │
              └───────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                                  ▼
              ┌─ STEP 5: Scene Prompt Generation ─────────────────┐
              │  Với mỗi group:                                   │
              │  → System prompt = Style (OverSimplified.txt)     │
              │  → User message = SRT text + Character Bible      │
              │  → Context trước/sau                              │
              │  → AI output: scene prompt (mô tả cảnh)          │
              └───────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                                  ▼
              ┌─ STEP 6: Output ──────────────────────────────────┐
              │  CSV: [#, Time, Original, Prompt, Status]         │
              │  + character_bible.txt                            │
              │  + character_sheets.txt (optional)                │
              └───────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## STEP 2: Character Bible — Cấu trúc mới

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Đây là thay đổi lớn nhất — chuẩn hoá Visual Bible theo **4 thuộc tính** thay vì mô tả tự do.

### Prompt cần hướng dẫn AI output theo format sau:

```
## HISTORICAL CONTEXT
- Time Period: [era + years]
- Geography: [regions]
- Key Events: [summary]

## CHARACTERS

### 🌟 PROTAGONISTS
[Name] | Chapters: [1-12]
- Headwear: black bicorne hat
- Hair/Face: clean-shaven, stern expression line
- Outfit: dark navy blue military coat, gold button dots, white pants, black boots
- Weapon: ornate officer saber at waist

### 🎭 NAMED SUPPORTING
[Name] | Chapters: [2,3,5]
- Headwear: tall black papakha fur hat
- Hair/Face: long white beard, bushy eyebrows drawn as thick lines
- Outfit: dark green Russian general uniform with red sash
- Weapon: curved cavalry saber

### ⚔️ MILITARY ARCHETYPES
French Infantry | Chapters: [1-12]
- Headwear: black cocked hat
- Hair/Face: (generic—no distinguishing features)
- Outfit: blue coat, white crossbelts
- Weapon: brown musket with bayonet

British Infantry | Chapters: [3-8]
- Headwear: tall black bearskin hat
- Hair/Face: (generic)
- Outfit: red coat, white crossbelts
- Weapon: brown musket

### 👥 CIVILIAN ARCHETYPES
French Peasant | Chapters: [1,6,9]
- Headwear: simple brown cap or none
- Hair/Face: (generic)
- Outfit: brown rough tunic, patched pants
- Weapon: none (may hold pitchfork, basket, or bread)

Noble/Courtier | Chapters: [3,7]
- Headwear: none
- Hair/Face: white powdered wig
- Outfit: ornate coat with gold embroidery, knee breeches
- Weapon: none (may hold fan, cane, or wine glass)

## KEY LOCATIONS
### [Location Name]
- Architecture: [period-accurate details]
- Key Elements: [specific details for background]
- Atmosphere: [weather, lighting, time of day]
```

---

## STEP 3: Character Sheet Prompts

Tự động tạo prompt cho Protagonist + Named characters:

```
Character reference sheet in [STYLE] style.
Stick figure with round white circle head, black dot eyes.
[Name]: [Headwear] + [Hair/Face] + [Outfit] + [Weapon]
4 views on clean white background: front, 3/4 angle, side profile, action pose.
Flat 2D shading, clean black outlines, muted earthy colors.
```

Với Archetype chỉ cần **1 view** (front) vì chúng generic.

---

## STEP 5: Scene Prompt — AI nhận Character Bible

Khi generate scene prompt, AI nhận:

```
=== CHARACTER BIBLE (REFERENCE) ===
[...danh sách nhân vật với 4 thuộc tính...]
=== END CHARACTER BIBLE ===

=== CURRENT SEGMENT ===
Time: 00:01:23 - 00:01:29
Text: "Napoleon marched his army across the Alps"

Generate a detailed visual prompt for this scene.
Reference the Character Bible for consistent character descriptions.
Only include characters relevant to this segment.
```

